That's why I tended to you
in the hospital for a week.

40
00:05:08,174 --> 00:05:10,574
We must accept that Zooni...

41
00:05:11,277 --> 00:05:14,007
...may have to live her life without
that special someone.

42
00:05:14,247 --> 00:05:17,080
That perhaps she will never marry.

43
00:05:18,751 --> 00:05:24,383
And when we're gone
who will look out for her?

44
00:05:25,124 --> 00:05:27,251
We must give her the
chance to live her life.

45
00:05:28,261 --> 00:05:32,095
We need to support her independence.

46
00:05:32,699 --> 00:05:36,897
Be her strength, not her weakness.

47
00:05:57,090 --> 00:05:58,352
Madam Mehbooba

48
00:05:58,758 --> 00:06:01,454
Bobo, the name is Bobo not Mehbooba

49
00:06:01,661 --> 00:06:03,128
Whatever you command your highness.

50
00:06:03,329 --> 00:06:05,957
By the way, your bags weigh
more than your brain!

51
00:06:06,332 --> 00:06:08,960
Obviously! Haven't you heard that saying?

52
00:06:09,168 --> 00:06:11,693
- Which one?
- "The buffalo is bigger than the brain."

53
00:06:12,004 --> 00:06:14,131
No dummy, it's "Is the brain bigger
or the buffalo?"

54
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:16,308
- Fatty!
- Not Fatty, Fatima.

55
00:06:16,509 --> 00:06:18,909
