even they will be born bent over.

116
00:09:48,554 --> 00:09:50,579
I have no interest in your
family planning program!

117
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:51,779
Where is that tour guide?

118
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:04,427
I am the Balwaan.
Not the Cartoon Network.

119
00:10:04,637 --> 00:10:06,127
You are exactly what you look like!

120
00:10:06,405 --> 00:10:07,599
Now tell me what's the problem here?

121
00:10:08,574 --> 00:10:09,871
Where do I start?

122
00:10:10,176 --> 00:10:11,200
From the head light to the exhaust...

123
00:10:11,410 --> 00:10:13,275
...there are problems and more problems.

124
00:10:17,917 --> 00:10:20,647
